Helan Mountains, located in northwest China, is known for a large number of blue sheep living there. It also turns into a great sight when it's covered with snow. In this video taken this month in Ningxia Hui Autonomous Region by photographer Liu Yufei, you can see the beautiful Helan Mountains covered with snow against the blue sky. (The video is provided by Liu Yufei.) (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)